Interview Questions

Q. groupingBy() kya return karta hai?

Ans: Default me Map<K, List<T>>.

Q. Kya key kisi property se banti hai?

Ans: Haan, classifier function (jaise Student::getDepartment) se.

Q. Kya custom collector ke saath use kar sakte hain?

Ans: Haan. Jaise:

Collectors.groupingBy(
    Student::getDepartment,
    Collectors.counting()
)

Isse har department me kitne students hain, woh milega.

Common Mistakes

❌ Sochna ki groupingBy() list ko sort karta hai.

➡️ Nahi, ye sirf group banata hai.

❌ Sochna ki output List hota hai.

➡️ Output Map hota hai.

❌ Mutable objects ko group karne ke baad unhe bina soche modify karna.

➡️ Agar grouped data share ho raha ho to unexpected behavior aa sakta hai.
